column3: Use these tables to ensure that your preferred UPS service option is available, and to identify the zone number for your shipment.  Zones are used to calculate the cost of your shipment.
Only available for the postal codes or cities listed below

To determine if a service option is available from your chosen origin postal code to your destination, visit the 'Calculate Time and Cost' tool on the  Russia home page at www.ups.com or call your local UPS office.
